1977;;Run for the Roses;;American;;Henry Levin;;Vera Miles, Stuart Whitman, Lisa Eilbacher;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Run_for_the_Roses_(film);;A young boy named Juanito Hernandez befriends and nurses back to health a horse that undergoes an operation. When the horse recovers, owner Clarissa Stewart and her trainer, Charlie, come to believe Juanito's hunch that the recovered horse now has a good chance to win the Kentucky Derby.